        <step1>
            <para count="1">If the voltages
                <emph type="bold">are not</emph>
                within limits, a faulty sensor, connector or wiring harness is indicated and further testing is
                required.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">If the voltages are within limits, the pyrometer gauge should be checked for a sticky needle
                (refer to
                <emph type="bold">
                    <hotlnk document="s08034x_25.xml" xrefid="x0803405">Restricted Needle Movement</hotlnk>
                </emph>
                ).
            </para>
            <step2>
                <para count="1">The needle sticks, replace the Pyrometer gauge.</para>
            </step2>
            <step2>
                <para count="1">The needle moves freely, check internal voltage.</para>
            </step2>
        </step1>
